dct_description_sm: Geological Survey of New Jersey. Atlas Sheet 29 (1914) New Jersey Geological Survey Relief shown by 10 ft. contour interval and spot heights. Depth of water shown by fathom in feet at low tide. Title is not given. Region covered: Monmouth Shore. Original survey and revisions to 1884, resurveyed and reengraved 1909, revised 1914.
dct_publisher_sm: Trenton, N.J. : Geological Survey of New Jersey, 1914.
